gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Spurs 118, Trail Blazers 105
gameRecap.excerpt: The Spurs defeated the Trail Blazers, 118-105. Victor Wembanyama recorded 30 points, six rebounds, six assists, and seven blocks for the Spurs, with Jeremy Sochan adding 16 points and seven rebounds in the victory. Scoot Henderson tallied a career-high 25 points, along with three rebounds and four assists for the Trail Blazers in the losing effort. The Spurs improve to 5-25 in the regular season, while the Trail Blazers fall to 8-22.
